{"type":"message","id":"490c1d93","parentId":"efb508b2","timestamp":"2026-04-28T04:04:43.206Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Gmail has no new emails in the last hour. For iCloud, I see 4 emails but they all appear to be from today or earlier. Let me check the dates more carefully:\n\n- ID 9: 2026-04-27 19:06 - this is from yesterday (April 27), could be within the last hour depending on the timezone\n- ID 8: 2026-04-27 12:20 - from yesterday\n- ID 7: 2026-04-13 - older\n- ID 6: 2026-01-22 - old\n\nThe current time is April 28, 2026 at 12:04 AM (America/New_York). \n\nI need to account for timezone differences since himalaya is showing UTC times. April 27 19:06 UTC converts to April 27 15:06 EDT, which means ID 9 arrived about 9 hours ago, not within the last hour. So none of these iCloud emails are actually recent enough to qualify as new.","thinkingSignature":"99e7e8dee2dd0f30bc79b0395e6984644604e4792e4444e29b192481133a1b63"},{"type":"text","text":"No new Gmail emails. Let me read the iCloud emails to check if any are from within the last hour:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ikz8xiwzvhi5_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"for id in 9 8; do echo \"=== ID $id ===\"; himalaya message read $id --account icloud 2>&1 | grep -v WARN | head -30; echo; done"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":953,"output":312,"cacheRead":19036,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20301,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777349076095,"responseId":"063f64d4111471e38b57804f0e1b46d3"}}
{"type":"message","id":"107de70c","parentId":"490c1d93","timestamp":"2026-04-28T04:04:44.966Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ikz8xiwzvhi5_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== ID 9 ===\nFrom: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nTo: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nHello,\n\nOk sounds good. I may have one for that time frame. Just keep in mind they are first come first serve. Once approved, your application stays with us until we can link you to a unit. Once Logan is done, we can begin the process. Any questions feel free to reach out.\n\n\nAmy Smith\n\nLeasing Agent\n\nT  |  845.452.3450 x312\nE  |  RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\n\nW | royalcoveapts.com\n\n\n\n[A picture containing text, font, screenshot, graphics  Description automatically generated]\n\n\n\n________________________________\nFrom: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSent: Monday, April 27, 2026 12:17 PM\nTo: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\n\n=== ID 8 ===\nFrom: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nTo: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nGood Morning,\n\nOnce Logan completes his, I can run the apps. When are you looking to move by so I can make sure I will have one Available?\n\n\nAmy Smith\n\nLeasing Agent\n\nT  |  845.452.3450 x312\nE  |  RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\n\nW | royalcoveapts.com\n\n\n\n[A picture containing text, font, screenshot, graphics  Description automatically generated]\n\n\n\n________________________________\nFrom: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSent: Saturday, April 25, 2026 1:49 PM\nTo: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1731,"aggregated":"=== ID 9 ===\nFrom: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nTo: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nHello,\n\nOk sounds good. I may have one for that time frame. Just keep in mind they are first come first serve. Once approved, your application stays with us until we can link you to a unit. Once Logan is done, we can begin the process. Any questions feel free to reach out.\n\n\nAmy Smith\n\nLeasing Agent\n\nT  |  845.452.3450 x312\nE  |  RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\n\nW | royalcoveapts.com\n\n\n\n[A picture containing text, font, screenshot, graphics  Description automatically generated]\n\n\n\n________________________________\nFrom: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSent: Monday, April 27, 2026 12:17 PM\nTo: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\n\n=== ID 8 ===\nFrom: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nTo: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nGood Morning,\n\nOnce Logan completes his, I can run the apps. When are you looking to move by so I can make sure I will have one Available?\n\n\nAmy Smith\n\nLeasing Agent\n\nT  |  845.452.3450 x312\nE  |  RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\n\nW | royalcoveapts.com\n\n\n\n[A picture containing text, font, screenshot, graphics  Description automatically generated]\n\n\n\n________________________________\nFrom: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSent: Saturday, April 25, 2026 1:49 PM\nTo: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment","cwd":"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-emmy"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777349084966}}
{"type":"message","id":"83f5b003","parentId":"107de70c","timestamp":"2026-04-28T04:04:49.807Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Both iCloud emails are from RC Leasing about apartment searching. The timestamps show:\n- ID 9: April 27, 2026 at 15:06 UTC = 11:06 AM EDT (yesterday)\n- ID 8: April 27, 2026 at 12:20 UTC = 8:20 AM EDT (yesterday)\n\nThese are all more than 1 hour old. So there are no emails from the last hour in either Gmail or iCloud.\n\nCurrent time is April 28, 2026 12:04 AM EDT - wait, that's 04:04 UTC. So ID 9 from April 27 19:06 UTC = April 27 15:06 EDT. That was about 9 hours ago.\n\n\nBoth services are clear—no new messages in the past hour.","thinkingSignature":"5303988f7b8cc59f2cfdf28e14cd4955b37643ad22add2b9fd477f097ecd11d1"},{"type":"text","text":"📬 GMAIL — No new emails\n\n📬 ICLOUD — No new emails"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1730,"output":192,"cacheRead":19036,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20958,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777349084968,"responseId":"063f64dd9e3a37fdc9f197ba2bfda6b8"}}
